{"tid":2365802,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完民間電視個投票走勢，發現其實各位並唔抗拒睇大台劇集","createTime":"2021-01-14T04:52:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T16:39:36.000Z","uid":261965,"like":8,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"215f08df71238caa68b9c6e76ae7a3a496eed980","tid":2365802,"uid":261965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:52:05.000Z","msg":"大佬 咩都男排女將<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係話佢唔好睇 但其實佢個劇本都係啲老土套路黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然係真人真事改編 事實又真係咁老土用奮鬥同堅持由丙組足球打到上甲一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但大台近幾年間唔中都有咁既質素既劇本啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n究竟你地有冇諗過自己唔再睇大台既原因係咩？垃圾劇本？黎黎去去都係個幾個人做？政治立場？定純粹跟風？<br />\n<br />\n個人認為二月廿九同歎息橋質素高啲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尤其是二月廿九 我諗係佢開始先帶咗咁多人開始睇viu既劇集 當年綠豆以至教束其實都唔多人睇viu...<br />\n<br />\n節錄我覺得唔合理/可惜既投票走勢:<br />\n<br />\n講攝影講劇本 有咩可能二月廿九同歎息橋差過男排女將<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9xoajPz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9xoajPz.jpg&h=f25242d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CeTajO8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCeTajO8.jpg&h=445b3793&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n洗唔洗一首歌都有兩個提名呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要兩首都前五<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />得Ronald叫座力頂得住男排女將<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兵佑作個首四年一遇呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都唔提歎息橋首Yours Truly有幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />始終偏門啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OtuQjQG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOtuQjQG.jpg&h=bdb31fb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又係力圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪人人都鍾意直接啲既情感抒發多過睇演員內心戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />二月廿九大把場都正過呢場啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有歎息橋Thomas對住Sammy剖白個場呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oa0sm5L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foa0sm5L.jpg&h=11f653d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個更加唔洗講啦下話！Yeesa兵佑家聰講樣講演技講入屋講印象深刻都係冇得輸！男排女將咩組合都冇可能挑戰佢地既地位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fr8EXYn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFr8EXYn.jpg&h=3204b71f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋可唔可以唔好咁多Mirror<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對佢地唔反感 甚至欣賞佢地上台表演不輸韓國男團 但而家係拍劇呀大佬 Ian點會係爭視帝呀大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Mirror幾個都唔係強尼或者張松枝個皮啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jSbrC2q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjSbrC2q.jpg&h=c8836689&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4LkW0fM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4LkW0fM.jpg&h=3da4faac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd23eb63aaf479ce35f362620642d70adc7d76ee","tid":2365802,"uid":261965,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:52:30.000Z","msg":"投票<span class=\"red\"><strong>最後今日</strong></span>啦<br />\n未投既/想改既快啲支持下香港演藝圈啦！香港都仲有好多好有heart既製作 就算你係唔認同我 覺得男排女將真係比其他劇都出色既 都去投票支持下啦 甚至你覺得大台有高質素既劇集都支持你去投 (始終太耐冇睇過大台 可能佢地真係有高質節目而我唔知都唔定)"},{"pid":"21677a6ba54877ef6af1bda600b326bcad36258f","tid":2365802,"uid":36481,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:54:47.000Z","msg":"二月廿九加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a0a0f049206dc4569823c9d09a10090e244dd8","tid":2365802,"uid":912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,